lead_paragraph: The Jazz would have finished eighth in the Western Conference with a victory over the Lakers and a Rockets loss, but Houston cruised past Sacramento.
abstract: Houston Rockets beat Sacramento Kings, 116-81, to clinch final NBA Western Conference playoff spot; other basketball news and scores noted.

headline.main: Rockets Clinch Spot as N.B.A. Playoff Matchups Are Determined
